WEBVTT

00:00:00.500 --> 00:00:07.000
is a transformative thing. If you read it, I hope you can get that sense as you read the songs.

00:00:08.500 --> 00:00:15.000
It transforms from fear to having this relationship to being transformed on the other side

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:22.000
to live freely. It transforms from isolation into intimacy and relationship. It transforms from shame to

00:00:23.000 --> 00:00:31.180
boldness. A truly transcendent experience of love will change your life.

00:00:32.180 --> 00:00:33.340
from the sexual relationship

00:00:33.340 --> 00:00:37.110
of who are our relationship with God.

00:00:37.110 --> 00:00:39.390
If this song is trying to indicate to us

00:00:39.390 --> 00:00:41.030
that you have to be fully known

00:00:41.030 --> 00:00:42.390
in order to be fully loved,

00:00:42.390 --> 00:00:45.870
there is a promise and a wonderful truth

00:00:45.870 --> 00:00:47.670
that we all can experience the fullness

00:00:47.670 --> 00:00:48.890
of both of those things,

00:00:48.890 --> 00:00:50.590
that the God who has created us,

00:00:50.590 --> 00:00:52.630
the God of the universe who has known us,

00:00:52.630 --> 00:00:54.230
even from before time again,

00:00:54.230 --> 00:00:56.590
who knitted us in our mother's womb

00:00:56.590 --> 00:00:57.430
who has made us,

00:00:57.430 --> 00:00:58.070
who has seen us,

00:00:58.070 --> 00:00:59.710
who has seen every moment of our lives,

00:00:59.710 --> 00:01:00.470
who has been with us,

00:01:00.470 --> 00:01:01.710
who has been walking with us,

00:01:01.710 --> 00:01:03.630
that God who sees us,

00:01:03.630 --> 00:01:07.430
knows everything already, and fully loves you.

00:01:08.950 --> 00:01:11.950
Any moment of guilt, any moment of shame,

00:01:11.950 --> 00:01:14.670
any moment of, I'm dirty, I'm worthless, I'm,

00:01:14.670 --> 00:01:17.230
I'm unlovable, any moment we have like that,

00:01:17.230 --> 00:01:19.750
we have a need inside of us to say,

00:01:19.750 --> 00:01:22.830
we need to be loved, and God, the transcendent God,

00:01:22.830 --> 00:01:25.390
God, the excellent God, God, the most high,

00:01:25.390 --> 00:01:27.910
sees us, knows us, sees our shame,

00:01:27.910 --> 00:01:29.790
our guilt, our marks, our dirtiness,

00:01:29.790 --> 00:01:33.460
and says, I love you.

00:01:33.460 --> 00:01:39.380
And that is our hope, that hope of transformation

00:01:39.380 --> 00:01:41.700
from fear to freedom, from isolation to relationship,

00:01:41.700 --> 00:01:44.580
from shame to bonus, the hope that we have for that

00:01:44.580 --> 00:01:50.170
is to know the God who has sacrificed His Son for us

00:01:50.170 --> 00:01:53.010
and for us to be in that loving relationship with Him.
